StarEnli-DR16 Change Log [most recent changes first]
------------------------

15 Jan 2001
-----------
- Changed a few buttons on the slideout (max, stick, menu) to make them
  (hopefully) more intuitive.  Removed max_h, max_w from the slideout.

09 Jan 2001
-----------
- add move cursor to topright and topleft of PAGER and RIGHT_PAGER -- done 
- add check-button style scrollknob to iconbox -- done

06 Jan 2001
-----------
- incorporate sounds from Youngblood's StarEnliWs4.  Rewrite sound config and
  remove excess sound files -- done
- attempt to fix bug with horizontally resizing DEFAULT windows (black text
  background starts poking out the other size, still does it a little but
  not quite as much) -- done
- create AUTHORS, README, ChangeLog  -- done 
- create ABOUT/MAIN file etc. --done

26 Dec 2000 to 05 Jan 2001
--------------------------
- create FIXED_SIZE and SHAPED borders (based on TRANSIENT) and add to
  windowmatches.cfg --done
- rename LEFT and LEFT_HEADER to SIDE and SIDE_HEADER to be more consistent
  with most other themes.  --done 
- rename MENU_FRAMED to TRANSIENT to better reflect its use --done
- fix up appearance of MENU_FRAMED and BORDER_ONLY border styles [see
  PAGER] -- done
- rename misspelled files (*hilted* --> *hilited*) and revise appropriate
  imageclass definitions -- done
- rename LEFT_NARROW border to LEFT -- done
- make LEFT_HEADER more narrow; ditch LEFT_WIDE --done
- fix image flow-through in parts of LEFT_* borders [pixel work]  -- done
- create LEFT_NARROW border for Gimp etc.  -- done
- improve appearance of bottom black line of MENU_FRAMED theme -- done
- create new BLEFT_TOPRIGHT image class for LEFT_* borders to avoid
  confusion (created by using BDEFAULT_BOTTOMRIGHT twice) and to create new
images which merge better with the LEFT_* top border -- done
- add ICONIFY button to the default titlebar. -- done 
- rename WIDE_LEFT and WIDE SPECIAL to LEFT_BORDER and LEFT_HEADER -- done
- fix up WIDE_LEFT and WIDE_SPECIAL borders, perhaps conglomerate styles --
  done
- fix DEFAULT top and left borders so it doesn't look terrible around a
  small window -- done
- resize all slideout buttons and return them to the slideout -- done
- incorporate images and border styles from Canin's StarEnli-snapshot of
  01/01/00 -- done
- indicate sticky window -- done
- decide what to do with slideout menu -- done -- iconify; stick; shade;
  maximise_v; 
- change menu border config style so that you (mostly) don't get ... in the
  middle of menu titles
- fix background problem in virtual desktop settings and multiple desktop
  settings dialog -- done
- fix ED / TE /M* tooltip issue on navi console -- done. Generally ok,
  though still dodgy, but seems unfixable.
- use mouse images (TOOLTIP_ACTION_TEXT) in theme-defined tooltips -- done
- define tooltips for pager -- done
- define tooltips for iconbox -- done
- reorder slideout bar -- done
- clean up action classes, tooltips [use default tooltips]  and images on
  slideout bar - done
- clean up (remove) action classes in borders/common/borders.cfg -- done
- add CUR_KILL cursor to exit button
- fix ugly cursors (particularly on border top) -- done
- get border action class definitions out of slideouts/slideouts.cfg --
  done
- fix spelling in image names and image classes
- fix MENU_FRAMED, ICONBOX and DEFAULT border ugliness -- done
- make RIGHT_PAGER border style -- done
- fix PAGER shading -- done
- fix up listing of epplets, backgrounds etc. so they don't go off the
  screen -- done
- go through config files, cleaning up the comments and rogue #includes
  etc. -- done
- clean up action classes, tooltips and images on navi key -- done [navi
  key renamed navi console] -- done
- make slideouts go to the left -- done
- convert StarEnli-0.13/ to proper DR 16 compliance -- done
